      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/18/13",
      "text": [
        " : ذُكِرَ عِنْدَ عَلِيِّ بْنِ اَلْحُسَيْنِ عَلَيْهِمَا اَلسَّلاَمُ غَلاَءُ اَلسِّعْرِ فَقَالَ \"وَ مَا عَلَيَّ مِنْ غَلاَئِهِ إِنْ غَلاَ فَهُوَ عَلَيْهِ وَ إِنْ رَخُصَ فَهُوَ عَلَيْهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3966 - It is narrated from Abu Hamzah al-Thumali that he said:\nImam Ali ibn Al-Hussain (as) was informed about the rise in prices.\nImam (as) said: \"What concern is it to me if prices rise? It is upon Him (swt), and if they fall, it is upon Him (swt).\""
        ]
      }
    },
